title: Salsa's Taco Bar
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Beer/Wine, Take-out, Mexican, Catering, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Casual Mexican food eatery and cantina. Offers a separate vegan menu with dishes like vegan tacos, spinach enchiladas, flautas, burrito, chimichanga, sope, and taco salad. Fresh salsa bar. Separate fryer for vegan food. ATM on the premises. The owners will assist you with your order.
